room_title: Escape room "Escape the Mad Hatter" by Ryptic Room Escape in San Jose
room_address: 1931 Old Middlefield Way, Unit X Mountain View, CA 94043
room_description:
The Mad Hatter has you trapped in a never-ending game of musical chairs! Can you and your team solve the puzzles and escape...before it's too late?
This is a game with up to 4 teams of 6 players playing competitively, allowing for up to 24 players at once.
